}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCDXv4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCDXv4t.jpg&h=c2140d08&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>七區集會</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n  日期：8月5日<br />\n  時間：下午一時開始<br />\n各區地點：金鐘添馬公園、旺角麥花臣球場、沙田百步梯、大埔廣福球場、荃灣沙咀道球場、黃大仙廣場、屯門公園<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLCv36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLCv36.jpg&h=09ba4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKejKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKejKpu.jpg&h=f51b4d73&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7e6e9147ca05894a1dd12efa2e3ae78b6b6127f7","tid":1379653,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"82673637b04e30a3bb16fe7cbd7c373bf5144203","tid":1379653,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:52:38.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n不分化 不指責 <br />\n不被捕 不受傷<br />\n齊上齊落 一個都不能少"},{"pid":"fd73b7c6be5dbc39826845b66bfaa35b66054d5a","tid":1379653,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:56:16.000Z","msg":"今日新疆 明日香港"},{"pid":"f585f37b3bf1523b8d4f60a87592e54fa3131c85","tid":1379653,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"大罷工<br />\n唔係個個可以長期咁<br />\n但我相信只要全港冇包伏既人<br />\n齊齊唔做野,我睇下香港點運作<br />\n唔係唔返工都拉呀,屌你老母  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cb0793497a762af0af666ff8953a21bebd9681","tid":1379653,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"仲時咩代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立,別無他法</span></span>"},{"pid":"d181fafe9cfa7593c60d3550b980750eb92de572","tid":1379653,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f585f37b3bf1523b8d4f60a87592e54fa3131c85","tid":1379653,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"大罷工<br />\n唔係個個可以長期咁<br />\n但我相信只要全港冇包伏既人<br />\n齊齊唔做野,我睇下香港點運作<br />\n唔係唔返工都拉呀,屌你老母  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:28:33.000Z","msg":"咁食到屎啦"}]}